"&#xa0;\nWritten evidence from Susan Atkinson\nMy husband and I farm in south Notts, on an 80 hectare farm that has been in my husband’s family for over 90 years.  At present it is mostly arable and also in the HLS scheme.  My husband and I are also volunteers with the Farming Community Network (FCN).\nImproving UK food security&#xa0;\nPrice of food and costs of production&#xa0;\nThe implications of volatility&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nThe contribution of science&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nClimate change&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nMarkets and Production&#xa0;\nIncreasing self sufficiency&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\nDecember 2013\n&#xa0;\n&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;\n&#xa0;\n"